216
00:15:17,999 --> 00:15:19,969
"Jednoducho som ťa miloval."

217
00:15:35,350 --> 00:15:37,650
"Preto chcem, aby si verila jednej veci."

218
00:15:42,759 --> 00:15:44,630
"Si skutočná."

219
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:57,109
"Zabudni na včerajšok,"

220
00:15:57,109 --> 00:16:00,109
"aby mohol začať nový deň."

